{"tid":165361,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港沒有土地問題，只有人口問題","createTime":"2017-03-21T10:02:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-22T03:16:42.000Z","uid":66811,"like":47,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e849d883e965170e1c2d8d112272bd47654a43e9","tid":165361,"uid":66811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T10:02:24.000Z","msg":"香港早已超負荷：房屋、就業、醫療、交通、環保。<br />\n<br />\n講到尾，患不均、亦患寡。<br />\n<br />\n香港低質人口太多，不止消耗資源，仲製造問題。<br />\n<br />\n古人都識小國寡民先好，可惜好多人無唸清楚就亂生仔，以為咁先係美滿人生，結果造就呢個現代奴隸制。<br />\n<br />\n「一孩政策」先係中國第一大發明。"},{"pid":"98120c78e3c4660ee7a8037b9b910501a6b07167","tid":165361,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T10:06:09.000Z","msg":"荒謬，政府根本揸住嗰麵粉供應，自己推高地價。"},{"pid":"5a54991184799d3782ceb8d47e2d32ef5b6ca5db","tid":165361,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T10:07:01.000Z","msg":"多得啲偷渡嘅<br />\n當年生活唔好偷渡落嚟<br />\n依家都生活唔好又唔走返上去<br />\n講緊你全家呀"},{"pid":"55a7785254f598cb077fcfadc6c1de7f8e7f9218","tid":165361,"uid":88739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T10:18:00.000Z","msg":"香港最少少二百萬人先冇咁逼<br />\n但係已經存在既人唔會突然消失架<br />\n除非一次過移民兩百萬人囉"},{"pid":"db10d8af36eba3b177ba22d1076b75ecc30977df","tid":165361,"uid":66811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T10:19:32.000Z","msg":"香港應實行一孩政策"},{"pid":"22c5814414714bfffbaae74dfdf88b97234e5ed5","tid":165361,"uid":30966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T10:22:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港應實行一孩政策</blockquote><br />\n唔關事 係班老野死唔去"},{"pid":"e32a11b4d3799f89c0f9fda6353b05b2af11e754","tid":165361,"uid":66811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T10:24:09.000Z","msg":"劣質人口<br />\n不論港蝗蝻都不應繁殖下去"},{"pid":"39e1e321357fdf62d8f128739715fb8bd3ec9a5c","tid":165361,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T10:26:00.000Z","msg":"正評<br />\n<br />\n標題精警<br />\n<br />\n但係出生率唔關事<br />\n<br /